
# Upstream reference clones (see upstream/SOURCES.md)
upstream/*/
!upstream/_*.sh
!upstream/_*.txt
!upstream/_*.tsv
!upstream/_*.py
!upstream/SOURCES.md
!upstream/_reconstructed/
upstream/_reconstructed/*/target/
!upstream/_reconstructed/**/*.rs
!upstream/_reconstructed/**/Cargo.toml
!upstream/_reconstructed/**/*.md

# Runtime snapshot of closed-source artefacts (regenerable from backend-bin/ and frontend/*-src/)
_snapshot/
snapshot-*.tar.gz

# --- 真实凭据绝不入库 ---
# `.env` alone doesn't catch `dev.env` / `prod.env` / `.prod.env`, so
# we also exclude `*.env` wholesale and whitelist the documented
# template variants.
.env
.env.*
*.env
!.env.example
!*.env.example
!.env.sample
!.env.template
*.secret
*.key
!*.pub.key

# --- 本次会话的临时清单（含真实 key，必须排除）---
APPLY_LIST.md
PRODUCTION_CREDENTIALS.md

# --- 反编译二进制（3.4 GB，仅作本地参考）---
backend-bin/

# --- 反编译/反混淆前端 bundle（含第三方硬编码密钥，仅本地分析）---
# 规则：只保留我们重建的 `<name>-oss/` 和上游克隆 `<name>-github/`。
# 所有 `<name>/`（原始 minified bundle）+ `<name>-src/`（反混淆输出）
# 都不入库——它们含 Stripe/Firebase/Google OAuth 等第三方嵌入密钥。
_archived/

# 反混淆 dump（通配所有 -src 后缀）
frontend/*-src/

# 原始 minified bundle（每个都有对应 -oss 干净重写版）
frontend/auto-dex-site/
frontend/blinks-miniapp/
frontend/bomb-fun-site/
frontend/huehub-dex-site/
frontend/payment-specifications/
frontend/payment-swagger/
